{"tid":1817112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[代人爆料]元朗區鄉黑區議員鄧鎔耀搞謝票宴","createTime":"2020-01-08T19:49:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T03:47:46.000Z","uid":61954,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2806172d634dc326ef3540740d1b181e5d5c4765","tid":1817112,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T19:49:05.000Z","msg":"<strong>事先聲明，我只係代人出post，我唔係叫大家去打攪佢哋</strong><br />\n<br />\n眾所鳩知，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>鄧鎔耀</span></strong>成功連任元朗(八鄉北)區議員，咁多鄉黑幫手投佢票，自然要搞個謝票宴慰勞一班鄉黑<br />\n咁我朋友收到風，[/red][/b]鄧鎔耀[/red][/b]個仔1月16號係如心廣場搞婚宴，不過係咁叫人唔洗做人情，因為佢借個仔結婚黎謝票，同慰勞7月21號當日有份幫手出黎嘅白衣人，當中包括佢親細佬<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鄧威良</span></strong>同另一村長<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鄧英斌</span></strong>，<strong>希望大家唔好打攪到佢哋</strong><br />\n仲有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鄧英斌</span></strong>較早之前被捕，係因為<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鄧鎔耀</span></strong>要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鄧英斌</span></strong>先做佢細佬<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鄧威良</span></strong>替死鬼，交人比警方交代，因為<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鄧鎔耀</span></strong>同<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">何君堯</span></strong>嘅勢力關係已經傾掂數，佢地一定唔會被入罪，所以佢細佬先可以逍遙法外<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>鄧鎔耀</span></strong>表示一啲都唔怕俾人徹查721事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://fbwat.ch/1dQm34yJoLmAQwm8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbwat.ch%2F1dQm34yJoLmAQwm8&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF0xTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=94878285\" target=\"_blank\">https://fbwat.ch/1dQm34yJoLmAQwm8</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>重新聲明，我只係代人出post，我唔係叫大家去打攪佢哋</strong><br />\n<br />\n左 鄧鎔耀 右 鄧威良<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MbfZkhc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMbfZkhc.jpg&h=00f46b4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n何君堯同鄧威良握手<br />\n<img s